-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LEDA
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version:        1.0

Description:    Library Extension for Data Analysis

UpdateRecord:   
  2005/02/10    K.Fujii   (v.1.0)	Separated from Satellites

Usage:

[0] Set some environmental variables for ROOT

$ export ROOTSYS=/opt/root/pro
$ export LCBASEDIR=/proj/soft/lcbase/pro
$ export LEDAROOT=/proj/soft/leda/pro
$ export PATH=$PATH:$LCBASEDIR/bin:$ROOTSYS/bin
$ export IMAKEINCLUDE=-I$LCBASEDIR
$ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$ROOTSYS/lib:$LEDAROOT/lib

[1] Compile and run CDC analysis example

$ cd $LEDAROOT
$ make			# to build libraries


